xyz.fsgek.common.data

Interface GekData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GekDataOutput
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GekData.OfArray, GekData.OfBuffer, GekData.OfStream

    @ThreadSafe
public interface GekData
extends GekDataOutput
    This interface represents data adapter to convert or write data into other types.
